						               													<description>La Muerte has a job: kill people that has finished their time on Earth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But not everyone wants to die. Some people try to run. But La Muerte don't give up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;La Muerte starts the game with Wrath value 1. Every card has a &amp;quot;Run&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;Wrath&amp;quot; values. In your turn, you can play until 3 cards and sum the Run value to be equal or greater than La Muerte's Wrath. If you run, La Muerte get's more anger and its Wrath value is increased, according with the played cards. If you can't, you died. As ghost, you only increment La Muerte's Wrath, and helps it to kill!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When only one player is alive, he/she has one turn to stay alive and win! But if La Muerte, with the ghosts' help, kills this last player, nobody wins, except La Muerte!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
